01:03:26,169 --> 01:03:29,472
2. STIR-FRY MINCED ONION, CRUSHED GARLIC,
BOK CHOY, AND STRIP LOIN

1749
01:03:29,539 --> 01:03:31,240
His process is similar to mine.

1750
01:03:31,307 --> 01:03:33,209
-No, not really.
-No?

1751
01:03:34,110 --> 01:03:35,945
Since when have you been so brazen?

1752
