1775
01:04:20,423 --> 01:04:21,991
-On the top?
-…so he might boil it.

1776
01:04:22,058 --> 01:04:23,559
You're right. I knew you'd notice.

1777
01:04:23,626 --> 01:04:25,561
The master you buried alive
is different, isn't he?

1778
01:04:27,697 --> 01:04:28,598
I knew it.

1779
01:04:28,664 --> 01:04:29,632
Wow.

1780
01:04:29,699 --> 01:04:32,568
-He gets the ribs out.
-Yes.

1781
01:04:33,269 --> 01:04:36,239
Can you top that radish you dug out
