1797
01:05:08,204 --> 01:05:10,706
It's Chicago pizza,
but made with Napoli sauce.

1798
01:05:10,773 --> 01:05:12,241
It's an odd collaboration.

1799
01:05:12,308 --> 01:05:13,609
Napoli sauce.

1800
01:05:15,177 --> 01:05:18,281
-Scallops.
-Yes, he's prepping scallops.

1801
01:05:18,347 --> 01:05:20,082
Sam preps scallops.

1802
01:05:20,149 --> 01:05:22,318
-The meat is huge.
-I see.

1803
01:05:22,385 --> 01:05:24,053
Your mother buys

1804
01:05:24,120 --> 01:05:26,822
