1805
01:05:26,889 --> 01:05:29,325
Sam is busy prepping the ingredients.

1806
01:05:29,392 --> 01:05:31,294
It's taking him forever to do that.

1807
01:05:31,360 --> 01:05:33,095
It's been well over five minutes.

1808
01:05:33,162 --> 01:05:34,430
I'm running out of time.

1809
01:05:34,497 --> 01:05:36,999
-Abalones are ready.
-I don't have much time.

1810
01:05:37,066 --> 01:05:38,301
Abalones.

1811
01:05:38,367 --> 01:05:40,970
