WITH GARLIC AND OLIVE OIL

1812
01:05:41,037 --> 01:05:43,205
VENUS CLAMS ARE READY TO GO TOO!

1813
01:05:43,272 --> 01:05:45,041
HE PULLS THE MEAT FROM THE RIB BONES

1814
01:05:45,107 --> 01:05:47,243
-It must be hot.
-Yes, it must be.

1815
01:05:47,310 --> 01:05:48,844
I cannot feel heat.

1816
01:05:48,911 --> 01:05:50,813
Doesn't that mean you're unwell?
It should hurt.

1817
01:05:50,880 --> 01:05:52,315
AHEM

1818
01:05:52,381 --> 01:05:54,817
Sung-jun prepares the fruit salad.

1819
01:05:54,884 --> 01:05:56,419
Sung-jun makes Macedonia.

1820
01:05:56,485 --> 01:05:59,588
They're both working on an orange
at the same time.

1821
01:05:59,655 --> 01:06:02,258
The way they cut it is the same.

1822
01:06:02,325 --> 01:06:04,460
-You're right.
-They look the same.

1823
01:06:04,527 --> 01:06:06,595
-Wow.
-That must be how Italian chefs

1824
01:06:06,662 --> 01:06:08,798
-cut the fruit.
-Seems like it.

1825
01:06:08,864 --> 01:06:10,700
-Will you try to copy this?
-Yes.

1826
