1855
01:07:09,291 --> 01:07:10,393
-Balsamic.
-Balsamic?

1856
01:07:10,459 --> 01:07:11,861
-Balsamic vinegar.
-Yes, balsamic.

1857
01:07:11,927 --> 01:07:16,465
