1868
01:07:39,789 --> 01:07:40,890
Bok choy.

1869
01:07:40,956 --> 01:07:44,226
-That's Chinese-style stir-fried bok choy.
-He cooked bok choy in Chinese style.

1870
01:07:45,194 --> 01:07:47,163
He's putting that on the onion.

1871
01:07:47,229 --> 01:07:48,497
On the deep-fried onion.

1872
01:07:48,564 --> 01:07:49,565
Wow.

1873
01:07:49,632 --> 01:07:50,866
What's that?

1874
01:07:50,933 --> 01:07:53,436
-He's making it into a roll.
-It looks good.

1875
01:07:53,502 --> 01:07:54,537
That has to be good.

1876
01:07:54,603 --> 01:07:56,505
That's new.

1877
01:07:56,572 --> 01:07:58,340
He made that with an onion.

1878
01:07:58,407 --> 01:07:59,542
He rolled it with the onion.

1879
01:07:59,608 --> 01:08:01,777
-There's meat inside, right?
-Yes.

1880
01:08:02,912 --> 01:08:04,713
They don't have much time. Six minutes.

1881
01:08:04,780 --> 01:08:06,015
Six minutes.

1882
01:08:06,082 --> 01:08:06,916
WHAT'S CHEESE IN ROUX LIKE?

1883
01:08:06,982 --> 01:08:09,085
