1884
01:08:09,151 --> 01:08:11,087
-Wow.
-Is it really?

1885
01:08:11,153 --> 01:08:12,321
-"Wow"?
-It's insane.

1886
01:08:12,388 --> 01:08:14,690
-He made it and called it insane.
-It's so good.

1887
01:08:14,757 --> 01:08:15,825
He didn't even season it.

1888
01:08:15,891 --> 01:08:17,293
-It's amazing.
-It looks good.

1889
01:08:17,359 --> 01:08:19,995
Eun-yeong stood there
and also kept saying, "It looks good."

1890
01:08:20,062 --> 01:08:20,896
This tastes healthy.

1891
01:08:20,963 --> 01:08:21,797
BELATED EMBARRASSMENT

1892
