Apple cinnamon jam.

1898
01:08:30,506 --> 01:08:32,208
-Cinnamon?
-That looks good.

1899
01:08:32,274 --> 01:08:33,576
I going to <i>mantecare</i>.

1900
01:08:33,642 --> 01:08:35,111
-<i>Mantecare</i>.
-Jeez.

1901
01:08:35,177 --> 01:08:37,113
He can't get rid of that habit.

1902
01:08:37,179 --> 01:08:38,314
<i>Mantecare</i>?

1903
01:08:38,848 --> 01:08:40,316
I can do it too.

1904
01:08:40,382 --> 01:08:41,684
WILL HE SERVE IT LIKE THIS?

1905
