-That fruit salad has no juice.
-It doesn't.

1906
01:08:45,454 --> 01:08:46,822
A punch-less fruit punch?

1907
01:08:46,889 --> 01:08:48,557
It looks like cubed radish kimchi.

1908
01:08:48,624 --> 01:08:49,892
I'm not done yet.

1909
01:08:49,959 --> 01:08:51,794
